  "title": "Talent Acquisition Consultant, (Freelance) (Ref:GKK)",
  "description": "<p>Are you looking to take your career to new heights in a company that truly values people, growth, and impact?</p><p>At Celecti, we do more than just recruitment - we build lasting careers and connect talent with opportunity. If you're driven, people-oriented, we want you on our team!</p><p>We’re hiring <strong>Talent Acquisition Consultants</strong> <strong>(Freelance) </strong>who are passionate about making a\nreal impact through meaningful work.</p><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li><strong>You define your own earning potential</strong> — a fully commission-based model that rewards your performance, ambition, and results.</li><li><strong>Flexible working hours</strong> — manage your own time and set your own targets.</li><li><strong>Comprehensive training and mentorship</strong> to support your success.</li><li><strong>A supportive, collaborative team culture</strong> that celebrates growth.</li><li><strong>Continuous learning and development</strong> opportunities to help you excel.</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li>Create engaging job ads and manage postings across various platforms.</li><li>Screen, shortlist, and match candidates to suitable roles.</li><li>Conduct interviews and assessments to identify top talent.</li><li>Coordinate interview arrangements between clients and candidates.</li><li>Prepare contracts and handle all required documentation.</li><li>Develop and maintain a strong pipeline of qualified candidates.</li><li>Keep an organized, up-to-date candidate database.</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>A Diploma or degree in any discipline</li><li>A positive attitude, strong initiative, and self-driven</li><li>Tech-savvy</li></ul><p><strong>Ready to Make a Difference?</strong></p><p>If you’re seeking flexibility and a rewarding career with real growth, purpose, and impact, we’d love to meet you.</p><p><strong>Apply now!</strong><br />\nSend your resume (in MS Word format) to <a href=\"mailto:hr@celecti.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>hr@celecti.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><strong>Let’s grow together — at Celecti.</strong></p><p>Lim Swee Kim (Ms.) | CEI Reg.: No. No: R1103707 | Director | Mobile: 9011 1145 |Office Mainline.: 6385 6696</p>",
